      "DIY only makes sense if you live nearby, can answer messages quickly every day, can manage cleaners and maintenance reliably, and are willing to treat hosting like an active side business. Managed Airbnb is better for owners who want higher occupancy, fewer headaches, and more predictable results."
  }
